Description: Whole-brain surface analysis of FreeSurfer MGH format data. The package allows 
  application of several statistical models per vertex, including linear mixed models
  and vertex-wise meta-analysis. 
  It can handle imputed datasets from several packages (mice, mi, amelia, etc.). 
  Multiple testing correction is achieved using MCZ simulations from FreeSurfer.
